EXERCISE 12 on page 166:

This program prints a list of prime numbers.
Well, it will do so after you have completed
the code.  To see what the output should
look like, see the file named output.

To compile this program, you can give
the command

   cc *.c

If you have the GNU C/C++ compiler,
then you can give the command

   make

to compile this program.
